question:
If today is Monday, May 23, 2022, what day of the week will it be in 59 days? Write out the full weekday name.
Output final answer with the format <<<answer>>>
response_list:
assistant > code_interpreter

from datetime import datetime, timedelta

# Given date
start_date = datetime(2022, 5, 23)

# Number of days to add
days_to_add = 59

# Calculate the new date
new_date = start_date + timedelta(days=days_to_add)

# Get the full weekday name
weekday_name = new_date.strftime("%A")
weekday_name
assistant > The day of the week 59 days after Monday, May 23, 2022, will be <<<Thursday>>>.
